data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! This quad-level gem offers the perfect blend of space, comfort, and style. Situated in the sought-after Reeths-Puffer school district, this property is a true find. The listing agent is also the seller, ensuring a smooth and transparent process.
4 Bedrooms: Spacious and versatile
2 Full Baths, 1 Half Bath: Convenience with well-appointed bathrooms.
Family Room with Gas Fireplace: Cozy up by the fireplace during chilly evenings.
Additional Rec Room in Basement: Perfect for a home office, playroom, or entertainment space.
Laundry Room: Practical and functional, making chores a breeze.
Sliders off Dining Area: Enjoy easy access to the deck for al fresco dining.
Sliders off Family Room: Connect indoor and outdoor living effortlessly with a patio Large Fenced Backyard: Privacy and space for outdoor activities and gatherings.
2-Stall Attached Garage: Convenient parking and storage.
Brick and Wood Exterior: A timeless and elegant facade.
